'''第41屆倫敦影評人協會獎'''（The 41st London Film Critics' Circle Awards）是[[倫敦影評人協會|倫敦影評人協會]]以茲獎勵[[2020年電影|2020年電影]]的獎項，於2021年1月12日公布入圍名單<ref>{{cite web|url=http://criticscircle.org.uk/female-filmmakers-lead-nominees-for-the-critics-circle-film-awards/|title=FEMALE FILMMAKERS LEAD NOMINEES FOR THE CRITICS' CIRCLE FILM AWARDS|author=Rich Cline|date=2021-01-12|publisher=[[倫敦影評人協會|倫敦影評人協會]]|accessdate=2021-01-13|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112131300/http://criticscircle.org.uk/female-filmmakers-lead-nominees-for-the-critics-circle-film-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2月7日宣布得獎者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://criticscircle.org.uk/london-critics-name-nomadland-their-best-film-of-2020/|title=LONDON CRITICS NAME NOMADLAND THEIR BEST FILM OF 2020|author=Rich Cline|date=2021-02-07|publisher=倫敦影評人協會|accessdate=2021-02-08|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207202448/http://criticscircle.org.uk/london-critics-name-nomadland-their-best-film-of-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

